com.example.mooood

Class RelativeTime

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.mooood.RelativeTime

  • public class RelativeTime
extends java.lang.Object
    This is responsible to determine the relative time of MoodEvent (ie "3 MINUTES AGO" or "JUST NOW"). This will be used when a MoodEvent must display a time and date info in UserFeedActivity.
